OL,5, Those who have suffered will be at the 
OL,6, heart of the Covid public inquiry, the 
OL,7, chair of the inquiry has promised      
OL,8, during the first preliminary hearing.  
OL,10,FBaroness Hallett said the pandemic had 
OL,11,Fcaused suffering to millions of people.
OL,13,FShe said that included those who have  
OL,14,Fseen loved ones die, been left in poor 
OL,15,Fhealth, had education disrupted and    
OL,16,Fsuffered economic hardship.            
OL,18,FIt came as the inquiry holds a one-day 
OL,19,Fhearing on its first "module" -        
OL,20,Fpandemic preparedness.                 
